risk: low
confidence: high
resolution: Compare the governance runtime suffix with path.join instead of a POSIX literal.
expected_result: Package-manifest boundary tests recognize governance-audit runtime.ts on Windows.
actual_result: Native-separator test and required Windows CI workflow contract pass.
